text:
Pharmacy- Please scan your Que number or ID before take a seat.
Mobile payment and 1 hour registration.

Crowded polyclinic.

Managed to walk in to see a Dr by 9am, registered at kiosk at 7.40am.

Self registration via kiosk using nric bar code. Covid or flu cases will be seen like normal patient.

Remember to put on mask through out the time in clinic. Subscribed to e- payment through Healthbuddy app. Less wait time. Can leave after medicine collection.
Nurse SALLY KWOK was extremely RUDE and INCONSIDERATE. Challenging me to go complaint her !!!
Very old polyclinic but service is good, just hard to locate. Level 4 of Blk 163.
Long waits but clinic is clean and comfortable to sit in. Much respect for our public healthcare workers!
